quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  54,9,Kadhabat Qablahum Qawmu Nūĥin Fakadhabū `Abdanā Wa Qālū Majnūnun Wa Azdujira
  54,10,Fada`ā Rabbahu 'Annī Maghlūbun Fāntaşir
  54,11,Fafataĥnā 'Abwāba As-Samā'i Bimā'in Munhamirin
  54,12,Wa Fajjarnā Al-'Arđa `Uyūnāan Fāltaqá Al-Mā'u `Alá 'Amrin Qad Qudira
  54,13,Wa Ĥamalnāhu `Alá Dhāti 'Alwāĥin Wa Dusurin
  54,14,Tajrī Bi'a`yuninā Jazā'an Liman Kāna Kufira
  54,15,Wa Laqad Taraknāhā 'Āyatan Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,16,Fakayfa Kāna `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,17,Wa Laqad Yassarnā Al-Qur'āna Lildhikri Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,18,Kadhabat `Ādun Fakayfa Kāna `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,19,Innā 'Arsalnā `Alayhim Rīĥāan Şarşarāan Fī Yawmi Naĥsin Mustamirrin
  54,20,Tanzi`u An-Nāsa Ka'annahum 'A`jāzu Nakhlin Munqa`irin
  54,21,Fakayfa Kāna `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,22,Wa Laqad Yassarnā Al-Qur'āna Lildhikri Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,23,Kadhabat Thamūdu Bin-Nudhuri
  54,24,Faqālū 'Abasharāan Minnā Wāĥidāan Nattabi`uhu 'Innā 'Idhāan Lafī Đalālin Wa Su`urin
  54,25,A'uulqiya Adh-Dhikru `Alayhi Min Bayninā Bal Huwa Kadhābun 'Ashirun
  54,26,Saya`lamūna Ghadāan Mani Al-Kadhābu Al-'Ashiru
  54,27,Innā Mursilū An-Nāqati Fitnatan Lahum Fārtaqibhum Wa Aşţabir
  54,28,Wa Nabbi'hum 'Anna Al-Mā'a Qismatun Baynahum Kullu Shirbin Muĥtađarun
  54,29,Fanādaw Şāĥibahum Fata`āţá Fa`aqara
  54,30,Fakayfa Kāna `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,31,Innā 'Arsalnā `Alayhim Şayĥatan Wāĥidatan Fakānū Kahashīmi Al-Muĥtažiri
  54,32,Wa Laqad Yassarnā Al-Qur'āna Lildhikri Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,33,Kadhabat Qawmu Lūţin Bin-Nudhuri
  54,34,Innā 'Arsalnā `Alayhim Ĥāşibāan 'Illā 'Āla Lūţin Najjaynāhum Bisaĥarin
  54,35,Ni`matan Min `Indinā Kadhālika Najzī Man Shakara
  54,36,Wa Laqad 'Andharahum Baţshatanā Fatamāraw Bin-Nudhuri
  54,37,Wa Laqad Rāwadūhu `An Đayfihi Faţamasnā 'A`yunahum Fadhūqū `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,38,Wa Laqad Şabbaĥahum Bukratan `Adhābun Mustaqirrun
  54,39,Fadhūqū `Adhābī Wa Nudhuri
  54,40,Wa Laqad Yassarnā Al-Qur'āna Lildhikri Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,41,Wa Laqad Jā'a 'Āla Fir`awna An-Nudhuru
  54,42,Kadhabū Bi'āyātinā Kullihā Fa'akhadhnāhum 'Akhdha `Azīzin Muqtadirin
  54,43,Akuffārukum Khayrun Min 'Ūla'ikum 'Am Lakum Barā'atun Fī Az-Zuburi
  54,44,Am Yaqūlūna Naĥnu Jamī`un Muntaşirun
  54,45,Sayuhzamu Al-Jam`u Wa Yuwallūna Ad-Dubura
  54,46,Bali As-Sā`atu Maw`iduhum Wa As-Sā`atu 'Ad/há Wa 'Amarru
  54,47,Inna Al-Mujrimīna Fī Đalālin Wa Su`urin
  54,48,Yawma Yusĥabūna Fī An-Nāri `Alá Wujūhihim Dhūqū Massa Saqara
  54,49,Innā Kulla Shay'in Khalaqnāhu Biqadarin
  54,50,Wa Mā 'Amrunā 'Illā Wāĥidatun Kalamĥin Bil-Başari
  54,51,Wa Laqad 'Ahlaknā 'Ashyā`akum Fahal Min Muddakirin
  54,52,Wa Kullu Shay'in Fa`alūhu Fī Az-Zuburi
  54,53,Wa Kullu Şaghīrin Wa Kabīrin Mustaţarun
  54,54,Inna Al-Muttaqīna Fī Jannātin Wa Naharin
  54,55,Fī Maq`adi Şidqin `Inda Malīkin Muqtadirin